item.title: Motorcycle
item.description: A glimpse into the world of motorcycles University Of Waikato COMPX532 Jiahui Ding 1. Introduction Different from the tool attributes of four-wheeled vehicles, two-wheeled motorcycles (of course there are some three-wheeled heretics) provide a different lifestyle, allowing us to have a unique experience of wind and freedom. As the final project of COMPX532 course, I tried to combine the course and hobbies. Just like bragging about my hobbies to my friends, I hope that this project can bring a preliminary perceptual understanding of the world of motorcycles.
